sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor Founder
  participant Orchestrator as Genesis Orchestrator
  participant Research as Research Department
  participant Trend as Trend Research Specialist
  participant DB as Genesis Database

  Founder->>Orchestrator: Submit niche idea
